fields.name: Suspension
fields.description: 5 colour print. Printed on 250gsm Fabriano white paper. Each piece is a signed original 1/1. Due to the nature of the printing process, small anomalies and textures may occur (but add to the overall character!). The colours may differ slightly from the photography and are more intense generally on the original artwork. The bright red is often fluorescent and more understated on the photograph.
